​​Designed by celebrated architect Bayden Goddard, the modern four-level masterpiece occupies a rare north-east parcel on deepwater with unrivalled main river and city skyline views. An imposing concrete construction, stone feature walls and towering palm trees create a memorable first impression that's befitting one of the city's finest residences.
​
​See @Kollosche_ for more

A master wing with extensive private outdoor covered patio, fireplace, infinite his and her master baths and closets designed for today's royalty. Gated circular motor-court for 10 cars with oversized 3-car garage. Extremely private with endless and breathtaking mountaintop views.

Contact @misslhommedieu or @bachiroueida for more information! @1518belair
